data.description: Beautiful place to call home! Don't miss out on this one, 4 bedroom homes + bonus room with 3 car garages do not last! Fall in love with springtime flowers and fall colors, spend evenings on the covered patio or cozy afternoons in front of the fireplace. Imagine what you can do with all this space! Lots of extras here, Surround sound, insta hot water, laundry organizer, beautiful appliances, updated trim, fresh paint inside & out, built-ins, HUGE Bonus Room, new roof and more. AND - There is a 3% assumable loan option here, contact your REALTOR® for more info. There's no place like HOME
